	================================================
	Branch						Tag
	--------------------		---------------------
	-Branch is mutable			Tag is Immutable
	-git branch					git tag 		
	-git branch bName			git tag tName
	-git branch -d bName		git tag -d tName
	-git push aliasName bName	git push aliasName tag tName
	-git push aliasName --all	git push aliasName --tags
	-Create from any branch.	we will create tags on master/main branch only.(IMP)


	git tag --> It will display the tags
	git tag <TN> --> It will create the tag
	git push az tag <TN> --> It will push the tag to remote repo
	git push az --tags --> It will push all the tags to remote repo.
	git tag -d <TN>
	
	--> Tags are not automatically pushed when you push a branch or use the --all option. The --tags flag sends all of your local tags to the remote repo.
	
